pageContext.claim: “They dream about Sleepy Joe Biden. They own Sleepy Joe. You know, they, uh, they gave his boy a lot of money. China goes -- they go to bed every night, and they say, 'Please let it be Sleepy Joe.' They would own the United States.”
pageContext.analysis: It's simply ridiculous for Trump to claim that if Biden wins, China will "own" the United States.
